{"_id":"4NsyjAhhilhIKCG4","name":"Tenue de bal","type":"equipment","img":"icons/equipment/head/mask-tiger-silver.webp","data":{"description":"<p>Une variante de doublet ou de robe fabriquée dans les tissus les plus luxueux, arborant des fioritures de haute couture comme des fraises, des épaulettes ailées et des manches gigantesques. Un masque en céramique en est l'élément emblématique.</p>","cost":500,"quantity":1,"type":"outfit","rules":{"distracting":{"key":"distracting","label":"EquipmentRules.distracting","custom":false,"compendium":"outfit-rules","journal":"KTlwNqk22ZQ9boK5"},"innocuous":{"key":"innocuous","label":"EquipmentRules.innocuous","custom":false,"compendium":"outfit-rules","journal":"G7VQ3b3wtONDVtcG"},"stationSignifierHighborn":{"key":"stationSignifierHighborn","label":"EquipmentRules.stationSignifierHighborn","custom":false,"compendium":"outfit-rules","journal":"hf6c77gAadUsw87R"}},"qualities":[],"trademark":false,"masterwork":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"BPfYY4elWDuh3FBt":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.cryptomancer.outfits.4NsyjAhhilhIKCG4"}}}
{"_id":"640anybr3KtqwTn1","name":"Grand manteau","type":"equipment","img":"icons/equipment/chest/coat-collared-red-gold.webp","data":{"description":"<p>Un lourd manteau à double boutonnage qui descend sous les genoux,prolongé par un énorme revers. Il est généralement accompagné d’une ceinture et/ou de glands suspendus à au moins une épaule.</p>","cost":150,"quantity":1,"type":"outfit","rules":{"innocuous":{"key":"innocuous","label":"EquipmentRules.innocuous","custom":false,"compendium":"outfit-rules","journal":"G7VQ3b3wtONDVtcG"}},"qualities":[],"trademark":false,"masterwork":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"BPfYY4elWDuh3FBt":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.F8ZOXtYfxn0KYewC"}}}
{"_id":"6WGtfgnHPGVxf0iD","name":"Tunique","type":"equipment","img":"icons/equipment/chest/shirt-simple-white.webp","data":{"description":"<p>Un long vêtement en tissu lourd qui part des épaules et descend jusqu’à mi-cuisse. Généralement associée à une ceinture par-dessus la tunique, à des collants, un pantalon rus ou une jupe.</p>","cost":25,"quantity":1,"type":"outfit","rules":{"innocuous":{"key":"innocuous","label":"EquipmentRules.innocuous","custom":false,"compendium":"outfit-rules","journal":"G7VQ3b3wtONDVtcG"}},"qualities":[],"trademark":false,"masterwork":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"BPfYY4elWDuh3FBt":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.TxfktVljsW6KuwQr"}}}
{"_id":"9TK9Au9agWUVFI7b","name":"Uniforme d'apparat","type":"equipment","img":"icons/equipment/chest/breastplate-layered-leather-blue.webp","data":{"description":"<p>Un uniforme de cérémonie composé d'une chemise et d'une culotte assorties, ainsi que d'une veste à revers dotée de longues basques, d'épaulettes à franges et de boutons en métal rare.</p>","cost":500,"quantity":1,"type":"outfit","rules":{"stationSignifierVeteran":{"key":"stationSignifierVeteran","label":"EquipmentRules.stationSignifierVeteran","custom":false,"compendium":"outfit-rules","journal":"hf6c77gAadUsw87R"}},"qualities":[],"trademark":false,"masterwork":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"BPfYY4elWDuh3FBt":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.cryptomancer.outfits.9TK9Au9agWUVFI7b"}}}
{"_id":"GOexbaNFh6IFlba9","name":"Armure de cuir","type":"equipment","img":"icons/equipment/chest/breastplate-banded-leather-brown.webp","data":{"description":"<p>Une cuirasse ou un corset en cuir souple avec des morceaux de cuir dur et bouilli qui protègent les tibias, les avant-bras et les épaules. Elle semble nettement moins formelle que la brigandine.</p>","cost":150,"quantity":1,"type":"outfit","rules":{"damageReduction":{"key":"damageReduction","label":"EquipmentRules.damageReduction","custom":false,"compendium":"outfit-rules","journal":"nTaOnuWJDu1Bnsrg","value":1},"distracting":{"key":"distracting","label":"EquipmentRules.distracting","custom":false,"compendium":"outfit-rules","journal":"KTlwNqk22ZQ9boK5"}},"qualities":[],"trademark":false,"masterwork":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"BPfYY4elWDuh3FBt":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.yPr3n9eVRITcreM6"}}}
{"_id":"KOvhboVIIs7QgB9m","name":"Harnais de bricoleur","type":"equipment","img":"icons/equipment/chest/shirt-collared-yellow.webp","data":{"description":"<p>Une tenue utilitaire composée d'un tablier de cuir ou d'une salopette en toile épaisse portée sur une tunique légère, fixée au corps par de lourdes sangles en cuir et des boucles de ceinture en métal encore plus massives.</p>","cost":150,"quantity":1,"type":"outfit","rules":{"alchemicalArmor":{"key":"alchemicalArmor","label":"EquipmentRules.alchemicalArmor","custom":false,"compendium":"outfit-rules","journal":"GZetsxBM31aIPKMP"},"distracting":{"key":"distracting","label":"EquipmentRules.distracting","custom":false,"compendium":"outfit-rules","journal":"KTlwNqk22ZQ9boK5"},"innocuous":{"key":"innocuous","label":"EquipmentRules.innocuous","custom":false,"compendium":"outfit-rules","journal":"G7VQ3b3wtONDVtcG"}},"qualities":[],"trademark":false,"masterwork":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"BPfYY4elWDuh3FBt":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.cryptomancer.outfits.KOvhboVIIs7QgB9m"}}}
{"_id":"NwwSi4aBLMdHrWMy","name":"Manteau de tempête","type":"equipment","img":"icons/equipment/shoulder/shoulderpad-worn-gold-blue.webp","data":{"description":"<p>Une variante plus longue, plus lourde et plus rêche du grand manteau, conçue pour garder un marin à la fois au sec et au chaud lorsqu'il brave les tempêtes sur le pont.</p>","cost":150,"quantity":1,"type":"outfit","rules":{"distracting":{"key":"distracting","label":"EquipmentRules.distracting","custom":false,"compendium":"outfit-rules","journal":"KTlwNqk22ZQ9boK5"},"innocuous":{"key":"innocuous","label":"EquipmentRules.innocuous","custom":false,"compendium":"outfit-rules","journal":"G7VQ3b3wtONDVtcG"},"smugglersLining":{"key":"smugglersLining","label":"EquipmentRules.smugglersLining","custom":false,"compendium":"outfit-rules","journal":"p8518z1XzQ3TH0IK"}},"qualities":[],"trademark":false,"masterwork":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"BPfYY4elWDuh3FBt":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.cryptomancer.outfits.NwwSi4aBLMdHrWMy"}}}
{"_id":"PcPC4713E4K3bUda","name":"Brigandine","type":"equipment","img":"icons/equipment/chest/breastplate-layered-leather-studded-black.webp","data":{"description":"<p>Cuirasse ou corset en cuir lourd avec des plaques de métal cousues à l’intérieur du cuir, avec des rivets métalliques parsemant l’extérieur du cuir dans une disposition protectrice et décorative. Généralement portée sur un gambison.</p>","cost":250,"quantity":1,"type":"outfit","rules":{"damageReduction":{"key":"damageReduction","label":"EquipmentRules.damageReduction","custom":false,"compendium":"outfit-rules","journal":"nTaOnuWJDu1Bnsrg","value":1},"distracting":{"key":"distracting","label":"EquipmentRules.distracting","custom":false,"compendium":"outfit-rules","journal":"KTlwNqk22ZQ9boK5"},"innocuous":{"key":"innocuous","label":"EquipmentRules.innocuous","custom":false,"compendium":"outfit-rules","journal":"G7VQ3b3wtONDVtcG"}},"qualities":[],"trademark":false,"masterwork":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"BPfYY4elWDuh3FBt":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.JbbuOkm3Wcp0zq9A"}}}
{"_id":"RXZP3QHn2D3PeFfC","name":"Habit sylvestre","type":"equipment","img":"icons/equipment/chest/vest-leather-tattered-white.webp","data":{"description":"<p>Un mélange de peaux d’animaux et d’enveloppes de cuir, rehaussé par des colliers et des bracelets encombrants, un pagne et des os décoratifs.</p>","cost":25,"quantity":1,"type":"outfit","rules":{"innocuous":{"key":"innocuous","label":"EquipmentRules.innocuous","custom":false,"compendium":"outfit-rules","journal":"G7VQ3b3wtONDVtcG"}},"qualities":[],"trademark":false,"masterwork":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"BPfYY4elWDuh3FBt":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.xInzGdLYiLajyRBJ"}}}
{"_id":"XhbgyPGKEukNBSyx","name":"Armure de mailles","type":"equipment","img":"icons/commodities/metal/mail-chain-steel.webp","data":{"description":"<p>Un haubert et une coiffe composées de petits anneaux de métal entrelacés, avec de lourds supports en cuir, des jambières et des bottes protégeant les membres. Une surcouche décorative est suspendue au-dessus du torse.</p>","cost":500,"quantity":1,"type":"outfit","rules":{"damageReduction":{"key":"damageReduction","label":"EquipmentRules.damageReduction","custom":false,"compendium":"outfit-rules","journal":"nTaOnuWJDu1Bnsrg","value":2},"distracting":{"key":"distracting","label":"EquipmentRules.distracting","custom":false,"compendium":"outfit-rules","journal":"KTlwNqk22ZQ9boK5"},"heavy":{"key":"heavy","label":"EquipmentRules.heavy","custom":false,"compendium":"outfit-rules","journal":"SpzoIovwFAZtsdtL"}},"qualities":[],"trademark":false,"masterwork":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"BPfYY4elWDuh3FBt":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.7dpQ1FqInCXhw97q"}}}
{"_id":"gpUHsFVd49Xp9OQO","name":"Robe","type":"equipment","img":"icons/equipment/chest/robe-layered-red.webp","data":{"description":"<p>Un corsage et une jupe assortie de longueur variable, portés sur une robe en tissu souple. Généralement associé à des manches larges, des ceintures amples et des sandales ou des bottes en cuir à hauteur de genou.</p>","cost":50,"quantity":1,"type":"outfit","rules":{"innocuous":{"key":"innocuous","label":"EquipmentRules.innocuous","custom":false,"compendium":"outfit-rules","journal":"G7VQ3b3wtONDVtcG"}},"qualities":[],"trademark":false,"masterwork":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"BPfYY4elWDuh3FBt":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.uJkxY1y2FVuX6jhr"}}}
{"_id":"kaTFaaQNrpSvY4NL","name":"Armure d’écailles","type":"equipment","img":"icons/equipment/chest/breastplate-scale-grey.webp","data":{"description":"<p>Un ensemble en cuir rembourré entièrement recouvert de rangées d’écailles métalliques qui se chevauchent, donnant au porteur une apparence proche de celle d’un lézard. Des genouillères et des coudières en plaques de métal protègent les articulations.</p>","cost":600,"quantity":1,"type":"outfit","rules":{"damageReduction":{"key":"damageReduction","label":"EquipmentRules.damageReduction","custom":false,"compendium":"outfit-rules","journal":"nTaOnuWJDu1Bnsrg","value":2},"distracting":{"key":"distracting","label":"EquipmentRules.distracting","custom":false,"compendium":"outfit-rules","journal":"KTlwNqk22ZQ9boK5"},"restricting":{"key":"restricting","label":"EquipmentRules.restricting","custom":false,"compendium":"outfit-rules","journal":"kJ6qJugS2COwo8OO"}},"qualities":[],"trademark":false,"masterwork":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"BPfYY4elWDuh3FBt":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.rRkx8Dv0kwXtUw8v"}}}
{"_id":"r55HIFBFhGyXRgMC","name":"Vêtements ecclésiastiques","type":"equipment","img":"icons/equipment/chest/robe-layered-white.webp","data":{"description":"<p>Une robe ample et fluide avec des manches larges et pendantes et une capuche surdimensionnée à l’arrière. Généralement accompagné d’une mitre, d’un gilet et d’une ceinture autour de la taille.</p>","cost":150,"quantity":1,"type":"outfit","rules":{"innocuous":{"key":"innocuous","label":"EquipmentRules.innocuous","custom":false,"compendium":"outfit-rules","journal":"G7VQ3b3wtONDVtcG"}},"qualities":[],"trademark":false,"masterwork":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"BPfYY4elWDuh3FBt":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.lq8qhC0WlUYaJCtZ"}}}
{"_id":"sXByu2dYoIQV8TxW","name":"Armure de plates","type":"equipment","img":"icons/equipment/chest/breastplate-cuirass-steel-grey.webp","data":{"description":"<p>Un ensemble complet en métal, personnalisé, composé de plaques qui se chevauchent, de structures articulaires flexibles, d’épaulières et de tassettes, façonnées pour s’adapter aux caractéristiques physiques du porteur ou les exagérer. Il est surmonté d’un heaume à gueule de grenouille ou d’un gorgerin montant jusqu’aux yeux.</p>","cost":2000,"quantity":1,"type":"outfit","rules":{"damageReduction":{"key":"damageReduction","label":"EquipmentRules.damageReduction","custom":false,"compendium":"outfit-rules","journal":"nTaOnuWJDu1Bnsrg","value":3},"distracting":{"key":"distracting","label":"EquipmentRules.distracting","custom":false,"compendium":"outfit-rules","journal":"KTlwNqk22ZQ9boK5"},"heavy":{"key":"heavy","label":"EquipmentRules.heavy","custom":false,"compendium":"outfit-rules","journal":"SpzoIovwFAZtsdtL"},"restricting":{"key":"restricting","label":"EquipmentRules.restricting","custom":false,"compendium":"outfit-rules","journal":"kJ6qJugS2COwo8OO"}},"qualities":[],"trademark":false,"masterwork":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"BPfYY4elWDuh3FBt":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.rA6t9FBpFZgH2a7R"}}}
{"_id":"upNTMvW4iGZgc3cf","name":"Pourpoint","type":"equipment","img":"icons/equipment/chest/shirt-collared-pink.webp","data":{"description":"<p>Une variante plus courte et flamboyante de la tunique, faite d’un tissu de haute qualité tissé en un motif en damier, à rayures ou en losanges, avec des boutons en bas au centre. Généralement accompagné de collants ou d’une culotte bouffante, et d’une encolure à volants.</p>","cost":50,"quantity":1,"type":"outfit","rules":{"innocuous":{"key":"innocuous","label":"EquipmentRules.innocuous","custom":false,"compendium":"outfit-rules","journal":"G7VQ3b3wtONDVtcG"}},"qualities":[],"trademark":false,"masterwork":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"BPfYY4elWDuh3FBt":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.5kHE0JXCKE6YfPCP"}}}
